al stratification, and we discuss how these stars fit\nin our understanding of the spectral evolution. Finally, we uncover significant\nproblems in the spectroscopic mass scale of very hot ($T_{\\rm eff} > 60,000$ K)\nwhite dwarfs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Aug 2020 16:48:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-07"}
