proposed and compared with traditional simulational results. Such simulational\nstudies and the proposed systematics of compensation effect are useful in\ndesigning materials for specific technological applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Aug 2020 09:06:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Aug 2020 09:22:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 28 Dec 2020 08:02:56 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 4 Jan 2021 10:11:25 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Mon, 22 Mar 2021 10:31:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-27"}
