g the Knight shift on the Cu site, rather than\nthe O site, which is almost blind to the spin fluctuation at the $\\mathbf{M}$\npoint as a result of the strong antiferromagnetic correlation between nearest\nneighboring spins on the Kagome lattice.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Aug 2020 09:51:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 Sep 2020 12:45:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-11"}
